{"tid":2339342,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"前《警訊》主持攜犬尖沙嘴度聖誕 二人拍攝遭警驅趕：話要告我限聚令","createTime":"2020-12-24T14:37:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T17:46:51.000Z","uid":16659,"like":51,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"c51cc1726bb9d0ef773fa59c7c6c74476a9da61e","tid":2339342,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T14:37:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/F4wYTqXuasIwD_ZoWXEEN1Kr7Jo=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7CWOMOS4DVFFNFWHBNO4OOCL2U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FF4wYTqXuasIwD_ZoWXEEN1Kr7Jo%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7CWOMOS4DVFFNFWHBNO4OOCL2U.jpg&h=a052c012&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日平安夜，雖然武漢肺炎疫情嚴重，更有2人限聚令及禁堂食等因素影響，但仍有不少市民到尖沙嘴一帶慶祝聖誕佳節，而警方亦有加強巡邏力度，在全港不時截查認為可疑的人士。<br />\n<br />\n有網民發現，《警訊》前主持人梁皓妤今晚帶同愛犬於尖沙嘴慶祝聖誕，但卻被警方驅趕勸喻離開，《蘋果》今日就事件向梁皓妤查詢，她以短訊回應表示：「當時我哋拍緊節目㗎，我哋得兩個人咋。（可有被控告？）佢（警方）話要告我限聚令，話我聚集人群，佢趕，我哋都走，費事麻煩。」<br />\n<br />\n曾隸屬警察公共關係科（PPRB）的《警訊》前主持人梁皓妤，於反送中運動期間曾在社交媒體上以「支那運動員」發表文章，又對「香港黑警 Hong Kong PoPo」的專頁讚好。今年4月中，梁皓妤以私人理由向警隊遞辭職信，正式離開警隊。梁皓妤畢業於香港樹仁大學新聞與傳播學系，於2014年加入警隊前，曾任亞洲電視記者。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7sp_stji00dRv1LUgBT9ot9VTHk=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/THGNZ63GO5FS5BOU2OJKSLKUD4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7sp_stji00dRv1LUgBT9ot9VTHk%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTHGNZ63GO5FS5BOU2OJKSLKUD4.jpg&h=59f5c059&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jBo8pyvqqHiDU6kkzqnAxiQRAN0=/802x600/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DKDLLLWRLJGXZKK6ZCEUAFR57I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FjBo8pyvqqHiDU6kkzqnAxiQRAN0%3D%2F802x600%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDKDLLLWRLJGXZKK6ZCEUAFR57I.jpg&h=375191ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/8s4jIliYo2xBoGCZsR8Kf4aLjh0=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FEWVTE223NFHBAESX2GT6LYIAU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F8s4jIliYo2xBoGCZsR8Kf4aLjh0%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFEWVTE223NFHBAESX2GT6LYIAU.jpg&h=3d1337b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3MHe-fLxsjce2wkcwTaHMG59M-U=/802x802/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BY73XPJPXFEJPDJJ5LVCEVBLTI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3MHe-fLxsjce2wkcwTaHMG59M-U%3D%2F802x802%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBY73XPJPXFEJPDJJ5LVCEVBLTI.jpg&h=17be70e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201224/H7KTDJEW3NDMHLUHQHLZPOH2NA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201224%2FH7KTDJEW3NDMHLUHQHLZPOH2NA%2F&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGtxZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=1aab6b85\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201224%2FH7KTDJEW3NDMHLUHQHLZPOH2NA%2F&h=7b043587\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201224/H7KTDJEW3NDMHLUHQHLZPOH2NA/</a>"},{"pid":"614da438b7e3eaa964efa89a5c9a49d13b71582e","tid":2339342,"uid":189523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T14:39:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/ass